Iron Chef America - Season 6, Episode 13




Symon vs. Bloomfield

Celebrated New York Chef April Bloomfield of the Spotted Pig takes on our newest Iron Chef, Michael Symon. Will Chef Bloomfield rise to the occasion and come away a winner, or will Iron Chef Symon defeat this local Chef? Tune in to see whose cuisine reigns supreme!




Original Air Date: 15-Jun-2008
